- Forking and cloning by hackathon participants for the duration of the event
- Building and demoing AI matching prototypes during the event
- Internal post-hackathon discussions within WE+, AAA group, and Soulware

NOT PERMITTED:
- Public redistribution of `data/` (in whole or in part), including but not
